Edwin Stanley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edwin_Stanley 0 Edwin Stanley (November 22, 1880 – December 25, 1944), was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 230 films between 1916 and 1946. He was born in Chicago, Illinois and died in Hollywood, California.
